{
  "stem": "24130.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't affected because it was only affected so much because we were afraid the Hungarian-- the road that my father would take-- he used to drive a bicycle to go to work.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the road that he was taking, a lot of trucks went there to the Carpathian Mountains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were up-- going to Poland to-- to the front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Hungarians, the Germans, used that road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- if they saw a Jew with a beard, they would throw things at them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father couldn't go with a bicycle anymore with that road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no other road, so he used to go through the fields and walk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were already, all the children, and we'd beg my father not to come every night home to-- because it was too difficult, in the winter time, especially.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- he would say, I work very hard and I want to come home because [SOBBING] when I come home, this is my pleasure to see my family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were scared he should come home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So many times he would sleep over because we had an aunt there living in that town and he would sleep over there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we-- if the weather wasn't good, so he wouldn't come because he couldn't come with  a bicycle, he had to come through the fields.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that's how much it affected, but he still was teaching there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He still got his salary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He-- it was-- didn't affect his work that way, except that-- the transportation, the walking, and he couldn't go on a train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that's how it affected him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Was religious community life affected during that period of time?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Were there any laws?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was affected.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
